playstore_details.title: Coinranking - Cryptocurrency Prices Live & NFTs
playstore_details.description:
Advantages
- The most cryptocurrencies available
- Many crypto exchanges
- The only one with non-fungible tokens
- Easy-to-use app
- Dark theme

Live crypto prices, charts, ranking, market capitalization & more. Most complete data on all digital assets, including cryptocurrencies, collectibles, and NFTs. Up-to-date information, clear interface & simple settings. 

The most cryptocurrencies available
Get price information of more than 10,000 different cryptocurrencies, like Bitcoin, Ethereum, Ripple, DDK, Bitcoin Vault and thousands more.

Many crypto exchanges
Accurate data possible thanks to the integration of over 300 crypto exchanges, such as Binance, OKEx, CoinDCX, Bitoffer, and CoinBene.

The only one with non-fungible tokens
Coinranking is the first price tracker showing data on non-fungible tokens (unique digital items). Explore collectibles like CryptoKitties and Gods Unchained.

Easy-to-use app
Discover all cryptocurrencies, exchanges, trading pairs, and NFTs without getting confused and overwhelmed; our cryptocurrency data is accessible to everybody.
